=== start ===
 OVPCASSS Personel: Welcome to the Office of the Vice President for Culture, Arts, Sports, and Student Services.
* [ ] -> continue_1

=== continue_1 ===
OVPCASSS Personel: We usually call it OVPCASSS for short.
* [ ] -> continue_2

=== continue_2 ===
OVPCASSS Personel: This office plans and manages student programs and activities across the university.
* [ ] -> continue_3

=== continue_3 ===
OVPCASSS Personel: Its goal is to broaden opportunities for students’ physical, social, moral, spiritual, and intellectual development.
* [ ] -> continue_4

=== continue_4 ===
OVPCASSS Personel: OVPCASSS is directed by Dr. Lincoln V. Tan.
* [ ] -> continue_5

=== continue_5 ===
OVPCASSS Personel: The office leads and coordinates initiatives that promote cultural, artistic, and athletic growth among students.
* [ ] -> continue_6

=== continue_6 ===
OVPCASSS Personel: It also provides essential support services to meet the diverse needs of the student body.
* [ ] -> continue_7

=== continue_7 ===
OVPCASSS Personel: Through this comprehensive approach, the university aims to provide a well-rounded educational experience for all students.
